Short build procedure for GCCSDK (this is temporary and be part of the overall
build procedure):

  $ cd <project dir>
  $ autoreconf --install
  $ cd <temporary build directory>
  $ <project dir>/configure --prefix=$GCCSDK_INSTALL_CROSSBIN/..
  $ make
  $ make install

To cross-compile: you can reuse the same 'configure' script:

  $ cd <temporary cross build directory>
  $ <project dir>/configure --prefix=<result cross build dir> \
     CC=$GCCSDK_INSTALL_CROSSBIN/arm-unknown-riscos-gcc \
     CFLAGS='-O3 -mlibscl -mhard-float' \
     --host=arm-unknown-riscos --target=arm-unknown-riscos

-EOF-
